ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: If you are interested in programming language research, yes.

If this fellow student is interested in formal methods, this is definitely a must. Reading state of the art papers is what one should do anyway but this course will allow you to interact and by this way drastically improve and accelerate your understanding.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This is rather obvious, I would like to work on related subjects so this course helped me to catch up a bit with what science in this field looks like today. This will be a valuable for my future research---even if I am not sure what will be my actual field.
